[[!meta title="peprserv - A repository statistics server for pepper"]]
[[!meta date="2012-03-20 16:16 CET"]]

I've just pushed the first version of a repository statistics
server to [GitHub](https://github.com/jgehring/peprserv). peprserv
is actually a Lua report script for pepper, utilizing the
[Xavante](http://keplerproject.github.com/xavante/) HTTP web server. The
main intention for this project is providing a backend for serving
repository statistics to other web applications, like repository
interfaces or bug trackers.

A live demo using [the official Git
repository](https://github.com/gitster/git) is running at
[http://jgehring.net:9000](http://jgehring.net:9000), and the source
code is available [on GitHub](https://github.com/jgehring/peprserv).
